{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require financial institutions to register LPAs online using an access code",
        "additional_details": "We believe getting and using LPA is an overcomplicated process that has been fixed by the Government through the introduction of an online service, but has not been taken up by all of our financial institutions. We think they have no reason not to do this.",
        "background": "Financial institutions have had time to adapt to using online Lasting Power of Attorney registrations through the use of access codes, but some have not done so.",
